query:
SELECT rl.id, rl.lojaId, l.nome as lojaNome, rl.gestorId, rl.dataVisita, rl.descricao
FROM relatorios_livres rl
INNER JOIN lojas l ON rl.lojaId = l.id
WHERE rl.gestorId IN (SELECT g.id FROM gestores g INNER JOIN users u ON g.userId = u.id WHERE u.name LIKE '%Fábio%' OR u.name LIKE '%Fabio%')
ORDER BY rl.dataVisita DESC
LIMIT 10;
